  <static seed="2493">
    <statement><p>Which number is greater, <m>2^{400}</m> or <m>4^{200}\text{?}</m></p>
</statement>
    <solution><p>Trying to calculate <m>2^{400}</m> or <m>4^{200}</m> results in very large numbers. Notice that <m>2^{400}=2^{(4\cdot 100)}\text{.}</m> Also, notice that <m>4^{200}=4^{(2\cdot100)}\text{.}</m> So to know if <m>2^{400}</m> or <m>4^{200}</m> is bigger, we only have to compare <m>2^{4}</m> with <m>4^{2}\text{.}</m></p>
</solution>
